Scumtown High | A Jaydaddy Movie | Official Trailer

Written as a one-man show, in true Jaydaddy fashion, Jeremiah Mastro's debut indie horror-comedy Scumtown High is relentlessly unhinged. After the brutal murder of Scumtown High's beloved star student Betsy Robins, Quinn Callaway and his fellow classmates are now at the top of Whiteface's list. They need to find out who's behind the mask before Whiteface finds them first.
